dct_title_s: Land Use Polygons Dane County, Wisconsin 1996
dct_description_sm: This polygon data layer represents Land Use for Dane County, Wisconsin in 1996. The dataset was originally published by the Dane County and Information Office in 1996 as Coverage files for each township. AGSL Staff merged the township data into a single countywide shapefile for ease of use. See the DATADOC.txt document for attribute codes.
